e morrer lutando.

12
00:00:25,181 --> 00:00:26,861
Estou à bordo.

13
00:00:26,913 --> 00:00:29,574
AGORA

14
00:00:50,464 --> 00:00:52,822
<i>Vai logo!
Sai daqui!

15
00:00:52,822 --> 00:00:55,076
